      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas, another version was landed:\n\ncommit 5e5dabac9eca8bc6ea516fb3ad53b8d74fe80a37\nAuthor: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nDate:   Wed Jun 29 20:49:24 2016 +0800",
