      },
      "date": "2016-07-13 06:58:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAlways a good idea to explain why a patch is abandoned.  In this case, patch http://review.whamcloud.com/21088 \"LU-8353 mdt: mdt unlink should lock before lookup\" was landed instead.\n\nIs the 21088 patch intended to fix LU-7117, or is that unrelated?",
