          "date": "2016-06-29 12:49:24.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-7117 mdt: mdt unlink should lock before lookup",
        "message": "LU-7117 mdt: mdt unlink should lock before lookup\n\nMDT unlink should lock parent before lookup child, otherwise the\nchild may be stale in use later.\n\nAlso enable osd xattr cache for LMV, because it's fetched more than\none time in several reint operations (which is used to detect whether\nobject is striped).\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I62fbff5172036dc52b5b59e79c620bdf795a242e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
